<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="has-navbar-fixed-top">
<head>

  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>

  <!-- for use bulma responsice viewport -->
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>인프런 - 배우고 나누고 성장하세요!</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.7.4/css/bulma.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.2/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-oS3vJWv+0UjzBfQzYUhtDYW+Pj2yciDJxpsK1OYPAYjqT085Qq/1cq5FLXAZQ7Ay" crossorigin="anonymous">

  <!-- for use bulma carousel -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma-carousel@4.0.4/dist/css/bulma-carousel.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar is-fixed-top" role="navigation" aria-label="main navigation">
    <div class="navbar-brand">
      <a class="navbar-item" href="#">
        <img src="https://bulma.io/images/bulma-logo.png" width="112" height="28">
      </a>

      <a role="button" class="navbar-burger burger" aria-label="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-target="navbarBasicExample">
        <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div id="navbarBasicExample" class="navbar-menu">
      <div class="navbar-start">

        <div class="navbar-item has-dropdown is-hoverable">
          <a class="navbar-link">
            <b><%= I18n.t("nav.title") %></b>
          </a>

          <div class="navbar-dropdown">
            <a class="navbar-item">
              <%= I18n.t("nav.category_1") %>
            </a>
            <a class="navbar-item">
              <%= I18n.t("nav.category_2") %>
            </a>
            <a class="navbar-item">
              <%= I18n.t("nav.category_3") %>
            </a>
            <!--<hr class="navbar-divider">-->
            <a class="navbar-item">
              <%= I18n.t("nav.category_4") %>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-end">
        <div class="navbar-item">
          <div class="buttons">
            <a class="button is-primary">
              <strong>Sign up</strong>
            </a>
            <a class="button is-light">
              Log in
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero is-medium home_top is-light">
    <div class="hero-body" align="center">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">
          인프런에서 가치를 높이세요.
        </h1>
        <div class="field has-addons has-addons-centered search_courses">
          <div class="control main_search_container">
            <input class="input is-large" type="text" placeholder="배우고 싶은 지식을 검색해 보세요." align="center">
          </div>
          <div class="control">
            <a class="button is-link is-large main_search_btn">
              <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="subtitle">
          배우고 싶은 기술이 있다면, 무엇이든 어디에서든
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%= render 'categories/index' %>

  <section class="hero is-medium is-bold">
    <div class="hero-body introduce">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="columns is-centered is-mobile">
          <div class="column is-9-tablet">
            <h1>우리는 성장 기회의<br class="is-hidden-tablet"> 평등을 추구합니다.</h1>
            <p>경제적, 시간적 제약없는 양질의 교육으로<br>누구에게나 성장 기회를
              균등하게 주는 것! 그것이 우리의 목표입니다.<br>입문부터 현업에서 활용 가능한 최고의 지식들을 학습해 보세요.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%= render 'posts/index' %>
<%= yield %>
</body>
</html>
